{"tid":347971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受阻逾6小時　港鐵至少被罰1,250萬元","createTime":"2017-08-05T09:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T14:27:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2efc97b48df01115622a8c65e7cd7f61fd90e2ad","tid":347971,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170805/large/1501925020_d878.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170805%2Flarge%2F1501925020_d878.png&h=c2299c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵9日內發生第5宗故障，令列車服務受阻，今次出事的是觀塘綫觀塘站，信號故障逾6小時仍未修復。根據票價調整機制，港鐵今次事故至少要被罰1,250萬元，金額於下年度用來提供即日第二程回贈優惠。<br />\n<br />\n受今次故障影響，觀塘綫列車要慢駛，額外行車時間一度增至15分鐘，約每8分鐘才有一班列車。港鐵一度要提供免費接駁巴士服務，疏導乘客。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行票價調整機制，港鐵每宗事故的罰款額，是依列車服務受阻的時間而遞增，受阻逾31分鐘，至少罰100萬元；受阻逾3小時，至少罰500萬元；受阻逾4小時後的每個小時（或不足1小時），再罰多250萬元，每宗事故最多罰1,500萬元。"},{"pid":"370d446afef1eeddca9fde1f623f9acfd8248c3b","tid":347971,"uid":4574,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"下年加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f440de57436f1e7d5dec3e645f19877775534d","tid":347971,"uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"上限1500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aeae9c4ca0a50af469a58aa0ddd6894ffbcacee","tid":347971,"uid":3363,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上限1500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵根本當散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edf15f326e479c9cb5b9908f15e27bdf3c4e432","tid":347971,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-0